&lt;p&gt;Here at Blackberry Hill we provide a caring, clean and comfortable environment for service users while they stay with us. To help with this service we are looking for enthusiastic and methodical domestics who are able to use their initiative and work as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position available is for 21 hours working Monday to Friday. The shifts are Monday 08.00 - 13.00 and Tuesday to Friday 09.00 – 13.00. The duties include cleaning and catering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience is not essential, as training in our procedures and processes will be taught on commencement of employment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sue Slade, Hotel Services Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sueslade@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0117 3784435&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are interested and would like more information about the vacancy and the environment you will be working in please contact Sue Slade on 0117 3784435 or Buba Touray 0117 3784663.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
